room_title: Escape room "Alice's Wonderescape" by Mystery Mayhem Escapes in Slippery Rock
room_description:
Alice needs your help! Once again she has found herself out of favor with the Queen. Alice has summoned you and your friends to help her sneak into the castle and find the way back home.
Of course, the only looking glass in the land would have to be located in the evil Queen's chambers. Luckily, the Mad Hatter has left clues that will help lead to your escape if you're witty enough to solve them. You'll have to decipher between what is and what isn't important. You only have 60 minutes before the Queens' Guard surrounds you.
